This paper discusses the security, energy efficiency, and communication capacity of wireless IoT devices, which are all related to the field of computer networks and communication (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the security aspect of IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also touches upon the system aspect of IoT devices, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the information theory aspect of IoT devices, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the machine learning aspect of IoT devices, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
